Notes:
CDP is a Cisco proprietary protocol that is used for collecting directly connected neighbor device information like hardware, software, device name details and many more.

enable
show cdp neighbor         (TO DISPLAY NEIGHBOR SWITCHES)
show cdp                  (TO DISPLAY INFOMARTION OF CDP)

---DISABLE CDP IN GLOBAL MODE---
enable
no cdp run

---DISABLE CDP IN GLOBAL INTERFACE MODE---
enable
configure terminal
interface gig0/1
no cdp enable
